latestIgtvVideos.caption:
How did digital print and production company ARC Document Solutions boost its new business growth by 133% 
year over year? By choosing the HubSpot CRM platform. Since switching to HubSpot, ARC has seen a 100% user adoption rate – so now, the entire team is on the same page. That’s a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

How does professional development and training organization Sandler Training empower its teams to hit their lofty goals? With a little help from HubSpot. Since implementing the full HubSpot CRM platform, Sandler has seen a 40% increase in user adoption –  resulting in more complete data for everyone. Now, they can focus on their #1 goal: coaching their customers to success. That’s a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

How did safety training and compliance platform @vingapp achieve a 360% increase in leads? By switching from Salesforce to HubSpot. With the HubSpot CRM platform, the Ving team can track the entire customer journey in one place. It’s no wonder they’re growing revenue by 96% per year on average. 

That’s a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

How did merchant review platform @ResellerRatings increase its new customer growth by 60% quarter-over-quarter? By swapping Salesforce for an all-in-one solution: the HubSpot CRM Platform. Now, they’ve got more time (and energy) to focus on what matters: helping shoppers make better buying decisions.

That’s a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

Scaling across the seven seas seemed impossible. Until this CEO onboarded the HubSpot CRM platform. Now she's making waves. Connecting fleets. And treasuring customers along the way. That's a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

How did the mobile ordering and payment platform @Mr_Yum_ launch in two new overseas markets simultaneously, *and* secure the largest round of Series A funding for a female-led company in Australia? By delivering delightful digital dining experiences during lockdowns and beyond. With the help of the HubSpot CRM Platform, Mr Yum made ordering feel like magic, and helped the hospitality industry thrive in a new normal. Today, they're serving 13 million and counting. That's a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

Every year, @wwf executes Earth Hour: the world’s largest grassroots movement for the environment. The initiative started as the symbolic action of switching off lights, but scaled each year to become a catalyst for positive environmental impact -- by harnessing the power of millions of people, and inspiring them to make the planet a priority every hour of every day. How do they do it? By keeping supporters engaged throughout the year with timely and personalized content – with help from HubSpot. That’s a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

The pandemic shut down RV dealerships and manufacturing plants. But demand for travel trailers rose like never before. @Airstream_inc found a new way to keep travelers’ dreams alive, until they could get back on the open road. With help from the HubSpot CRM Platform, Airstream delivered delightful custom content and virtual experiences directly to millions of inboxes – achieving record retail sales YoY. That’s a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

How do you grow your business from 0 to 121 locations in just 18 months? Just ask @handledhome, a home services concierge company that set out to transform the traditional moving experience. With support from the HubSpot CRM Platform, Handled was able to make moving easier for their customers -- and grow their business into 37 states across the U.S. That’s a #HubSpotSuccessStory.

Can a gym thrive during a pandemic? @crunchgym proved it’s possible. Their secret? ​​Crunch Gym Shorts: a value-packed newsletter inspiring people to keep moving at home. With HubSpot CRM Platform there to do all the heavy lifting, Crunch Fitness’ free trial sign ups spiked by 28% YOY, their email open rate doubled, and impactful reporting became easier than ever. Most importantly: They made a tough time a little easier for their community. That’s a #HubSpotSuccessStory.
